config BR2_PACKAGE_PARTCLONE_47
	bool "partclone (0.3.47)"
	depends on !BR2_PACKAGE_PARTCLONE_33
	help
	  Partclone 0.3.47。与上一项 partclone (0.3.33) 二选一，勿同时启用。
	  安装布局与参考 FOS 一致（默认 /usr/sbin）。
	  The Free and Open Source Software for Partition Imaging and Cloning

	  http://partclone.org

comment "partclone requires a toolchain with LARGEFILE+WCHAR support"
	depends on !(BR2_USE_WCHAR)
